<subSubSection id="0ABDED246375CE20927E65D761600D0F" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" type="taxonomic history">
<paragraph id="85BD185D030A4B85AD2E367014DDC5BE" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">Taxonomic history.</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7372C75E8D438EC6F456FF424A79114D" pageId="0" pageNumber="1">
Originally described by 
<bibRefCitation id="EE05CE193F785997207E883E0F5AAB9F" author="d'Orchymont, A" journalOrPublisher="Bulletin du Musee royal d'histoire naturelle de Belgique" pageId="0" pageNumber="1" pagination="1 - 12" refId="B86" refString="d'Orchymont, A, 1943f. Palpicornia (Coleoptera) VI. Bulletin du Musee royal d'histoire naturelle de Belgique 19 (60): 1 - 12" title="Palpicornia (Coleoptera) VI." volume="19" year="1943 f">
